name: Rocket
description: Rocket is an oscilloscope-themed robot who is part of the WebtrES club. With its soldier-class box body and classic buttons, Rocket stands out with its rocket arms and legs, allowing it to maneuver swiftly and efficiently. Its screen displays a mesmerizing snake design, adding a touch of elegance to its overall appearance. Additionally, Rocket sports a protective helmet as an extra addon, ensuring its safety during its adventures.
